article.description: — Will Johnston scored 29 points as UT Rio Grande Valley beat Texas A&M-CC 89-82 on Wednesday night.
article.headline: Johnston scores 29, UT Rio Grande Valley beats Texas A&M-CC
article.linkText: Johnston scores 29, UT Rio Grande Valley beats Texas A&M-CC
article.story: EDINBURG, Texa -- — Will Johnston scored 29 points as UT Rio Grande Valley beat Texas A&M-CC 89-82 on Wednesday night. Johnston shot 7 for 10 (4 for 6 from 3-point range) and 11 of 12 from the free throw line for the Vaqueros (5-3). Justin Johnson added 17 points while shooting 5 of 11 from the field and 5 for 9 from the line, and he also had seven rebounds. Dima Zdor recorded 11 points and shot 4 of 7 from the field and 3 for 4 from the line. Isaac Mushila finished with 26 points, 11 rebounds and four steals for the Islanders (4-4). Terrion Murdix added 15 points and five assists and Simeon Fryer recorded 13 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
